#: ../../modules/readout/readout_bitstring.rst:2
msgid "Bitstring Measurement"
msgstr "Mesura de Cadena de Bits"

#: ../../modules/readout/readout_bitstring.rst:4
msgid ""
"Using "
":meth:`with_sampling()<qilisdk.readout.readout_spec.Readout.with_sampling>`"
" instructs the backend to perform ``nshots`` projective measurements in "
"the computational basis and collect the bitstring counts."
msgstr ""
"L'ús de "
":meth:`with_sampling()<qilisdk.readout.readout_spec.Readout.with_sampling>`"
" instrueix el backend a realitzar ``nshots`` mesures projectives en "
"la base computacional i recollir els recomptes de bitstring."

#: ../../modules/readout/readout_bitstring.rst:28
msgid "**Parameters**"
msgstr "**Paràmetres**"

#: ../../modules/readout/readout_bitstring.rst:30
msgid ""
"**nshots** (``int``): Number of measurement shots.  Must be a positive "
"integer."
msgstr ""
"**nshots** (``int``): Nombre de shots de mesura. Ha de ser un enter "
"positiu."

#: ../../modules/readout/readout_bitstring.rst:31
msgid ""
"**expand_samples** (``bool``): Whether to expand the samples, by default "
"True. If this is True, partial measurements will be returned as \"0\\_\" "
"where the \"_\" indicates an unmeasured qubit. If False, the unmeasured "
"qubits will be dropped from the bitstring, so \"0\\_\" would be returned "
"as \"0\"."
msgstr ""
"**expand_samples** (``bool``): Si s'han d'expandir les mostres, per defecte "
"True. Si és True, les mesures parcials es retornaran com \"0\\_\" "
"on el \"_\" indica un qubit no mesurat. Si és False, els "
"qubits no mesurats s'eliminaran del bitstring, de manera que \"0\\_\" es retornaria "
"com \"0\"."

#: ../../modules/readout/readout_bitstring.rst:35
msgid "**When to Use It**"
msgstr "**Quan Utilitzar-lo**"

#: ../../modules/readout/readout_bitstring.rst:37
msgid ""
"Use sampling when you need the full bitstring distribution, for instance "
"to evaluate a combinatorial cost function, run QAOA post-processing, or "
"compute error rates."
msgstr ""
"Utilitzeu el sampling quan necessiteu la distribució completa de bitstring, per exemple "
"per avaluar una funció de cost combinatòria, executar el post-processament de QAOA, o "
"calcular taxes d'error."

#: ../../modules/readout/readout_bitstring.rst:40
msgid "**Expanded Samples**"
msgstr "**Mostres Expandides**"

#: ../../modules/readout/readout_bitstring.rst:42
msgid ""
"When ``expand_samples`` is set to True, the bitstrings in the results "
"will include underscores (\"_\") to indicate unmeasured qubits. This can "
"be helpful for readability, especially when only a subset of qubits are "
"measured. For example, if you have a 4-qubit system and only measure the "
"first, second, and fourth qubits, a sample would be returned as "
"\"00\\_0\" instead of \"000\", where the underscore indicates that the "
"third qubit's state is not measured."
msgstr ""
"Quan ``expand_samples`` s'estableix a True, els bitstrings dels resultats "
"inclouran guions baixos (\"_\") per indicar qubits no mesurats. Això pot "
"ser útil per a la llegibilitat, especialment quan només es mesura un subconjunt de qubits. "
"Per exemple, si teniu un sistema de 4 qubits i només mesureu el "
"primer, segon i quart qubit, una mostra es retornaria com "
"\"00\\_0\" en lloc de \"000\", on el guió baix indica que l'estat "
"del tercer qubit no es mesura."

#: ../../modules/readout/readout_bitstring.rst:77
msgid "**Output**:"
msgstr "**Sortida**:"

#: ../../modules/readout/readout_bitstring.rst:86
msgid ""
"Notice how the first result includes the underscore to make it clear "
"which qubits were ignored, whilst the second result is more compact but "
"ambiguous unless you know the measurement configuration. This would be "
"especially important if there were mid-circuit measurements, since you "
"might measure just qubit 1 early on and then just qubit 2 later, so the "
"position of the underscore would indicate which qubits were measured at "
"each step."
msgstr ""
"Observeu com el primer resultat inclou el guió baix per deixar clar "
"quins qubits s'han ignorat, mentre que el segon resultat és més compacte però "
"ambigu si no coneixeu la configuració de mesura. Això seria "
"especialment important si hi hagués mesures a mig circuit, ja que "
"podríeu mesurar només el qubit 1 al principi i després només el qubit 2 més tard, de manera que la "
"posició del guió baix indicaria quins qubits es van mesurar a "
"cada pas."

